{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "皮诺 第4话 “怪物”的真相",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "镇上的人",
            "context": "劳尔塔大人。\\n准备已经就绪，请往这边来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "辛苦你了。这就动手吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "他们消失在岩石那边了……\\n那种可疑的人所说的“乐园”大概……\\n不，现在还有比这更重要的事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "好，开了。打开隐秘之门的训练\\n还真的会派上用场啊。\\n我来看看这里面……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "什么，这是！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "都准备好了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "镇上的人",
            "context": "是的，主教大人。\\n按照您的吩咐，\\n“怪物”已经维修完毕。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "“外敌”务必要解决掉。\\n这是为了保护我们的“乐园”，\\n知道了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "镇上的人",
            "context": "遵命。\\n一切都如劳尔塔大人所愿。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120007_01",
                "120007_01",
                "120007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "魔兽们",
            "context": "嗷呜呜……嗷呜呜呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "是“怪物”！有这么多！\\n而且，在那边的镇上居民\\n也一定都……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "不……不管真相如何，\\n我该做的都不会变。\\n因为……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "1"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "圣德芬",
            "context": "我很看好你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "我第一次被寄予厚望！\\n圣痕，解放！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "住手。所有人赶快投降，\\n把手举起来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "怎么会，你这家伙……呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "真是遗憾……劳尔塔主教。\\n我从镇上的居民那里听到了\\n很多赞美你的话语……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "但这才是你的本性吗？\\n倒在这里的这么多“怪物”\\n也是出自你手吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "可、可恶……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "你没办法狡辩吧。\\n毕竟一般的主教不会\\n在这种时间出现在这种地方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "这道光……你果然是“使徒”。\\n你这天使的走狗，\\n害我为了解决你大费周章！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "我是使徒，那又如何？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "真是的话，\\n就更不能留你活口了。\\n我要不惜一切手段。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "上吧，“怪物之王”！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "怪物？",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "呀啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "哼，受到“王”的攻击却还没断气吗。\\n真不愧是“使徒”，能两次击退\\n“怪物”的实力不容小觑啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "两次……也就是说出现在镇上的\\n和巢穴里遇到的都是你一手策划！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "没错。来这个镇上探查秘密之人\\n都注定要被“怪物”吞噬。\\n这是为了维持乐园而做出的高贵牺牲。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "不要！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "既然你是“使徒”，\\n就算是尸体也能卖个高价。\\n毕竟奥兹本军可垂涎已久了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "这价钱可比贩卖教会情报\\n多得多了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "果然泄露教会机密的也是你！\\n啊啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "怪物之王",
            "context": "嘎嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "啊……我、我的弓！\\n脱手了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "哈哈哈！看来国军的技术水平\\n比教会的圣礼还厉害！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "就算是“使徒”，\\n没了擅长的武器也无可奈何。\\n你走投无路了，小丫头。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "话又说回来，“怪物”真厉害！\\n只要有了这股力量，我成为教皇\\n也指日可待。可得感谢国军呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "你这家伙……以为女神\\n会原谅这种行为吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "会的。因为知道了这一秘密的\\n小丫头将葬身于此——“王”啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "怪物之王",
            "context": "嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120118_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "劳尔塔主教",
            "context": "解决掉她。至少要让她\\n能安安心心地前往女神身边，\\n一招致命吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "怪物之王",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}